Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.80,0:46:15.10,SignalNote,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\\pos(280,520)}Děkuju!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.80,0:46:15.10,SignalNote,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\\pos(801,648)}Je doma.
